Class Collectibles

game.Collectibles
Direct Known Subclasses:
Coins, Key, Mushrooms, Point, Potion, Rock, Treasure
public abstract class Collectibles extends city.cs.engine.StaticBody
A SuperClass Collectibles with represents collectible objects in the game. Consists of collectible static bodies that can be collected by player.
